    "Details": "While orbiting the system of [[TGT_SYSTEM,{TGT_SYSTEM.Name}]], Darius grabs your attention, \"Commander, the contract from <i>Great Shotz</i> is available for us whenever you're ready to accept it.\"\r\n\r\nYou turn to Darius, \"Remind me, what are the known mission parameters again?\"\r\n\r\nDarius reads out the mission brief to you, \"<i>Great Shotz</i>, a Davion funded company, requires our assistance by intercepting a raiding party convoy belonging to a rival company.  If we are successful, we will be rewarded with OEM parts we will use to rebuild [[SCN_MW,{SCN_MW.Callsign}]]'s mech.  Shall I accept the contract?\"",
